						               													<description>Box Description: Fast and furious fun for 2 to 4 players. Ages 5 thru adult. Knock it and sock it! While you try to block it! Don't let the puck scoot through! Players drop a puck onto a spinning turntable and try to protect their goals.  Don't let the puck scoot through - because if you do, you lose a point.  Three points and you lose the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;General Description: Consists of a central turntable that spins when the game is turned on (battery powered); on this is placed one of the game's two plastic disks (large and small).   Players operate one of four plastic sliders that they may use to block the opening on their quarter of the circumference by sliding it back and forth, much like a hockey goalie.  As the turntable spins, the disk will bounce about the edges. Each player must prevent the disk from escaping through their opening by operating their slider.  Points are acquired for failing to block the disk from escaping, leading to player elimination.  Two plastic barriers are included to block player spaces that are either not being used or have been eliminated.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
